              <div class="inner-circle"></div>
              <p class="h6 mt-3 mb-1 font-2">5th November</p>
              <p class="h6 text-muted mb-0 font-4 mb-lg-0">
                Winners announced & Award ceremony
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div
  data-aos="flip-right"
  class="px-md-4 py-2 m-md-5 m-3 text-center d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center flex-column"
>
  <h2 class="fs-2 pt-5 pb-3 font-3">Details</h2>
  <div class="table-responsive px-md-10 w-75">
    <table class="table table-bordered">
      <thead>
        <tr class="table-dark font-3">
          <th scope="col" class="text-start">Date</th>
          <th scope="col"></th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody class="font-3 text-center">
        <tr>
          <td class="text-start">
            <span class="fw-bold">14th July</span>
          </td>
          <td class="text-start">
            Meeting with Bataan Provincial Health Promotion Board to finalise
            the 2024 Tobacco-Free Generation-Bataan Province, Philippines Video
            Competition
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="text-start">
            <span class="fw-bold">July-Aug</span>
          </td>
          <td class="text-start">
            Interested persons and groups can refer to
            tobaccofreegeneration.world and tobaccofreegen.com websites to learn
            more on this endgame approach. One particular focus should be being
            able to translate the TFG advantages
            (https://www.tobaccofreegen.com/tfgi-overcome-global-blindspots/) to
            your video to leave deep impressions, make an impact on your
            audience and be the winning video.
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="text-start">
            <span class="fw-bold">5th-15th September</span>
          </td>
          <td class="text-start">
            Register your attendance to learn TFG with Staff of Bataan Health
            Promotion Board (Sir Cholo Oliver Enrique and/or Ms Kyla Jenneth
            Miraflor) to arrange for direct learning with the visiting TFG
            International Team. The Singapore TFG International Team will visit
            Balanga City between Sept 16 to 21, 2024. You will attend one or
            more of these TFG sessions, have direct contact to present your
            ideas for feedback on how to improve your winning chance. Lastly,
            you will then officially register for the video competition. You can
            also register your interest with the local Video Competition Mentor,
            Sir Russel Sarmiento from Dinalupihan. (email:
            russel2017.tfg@gmail.com)
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="text-start">
            <span class="fw-bold">10th October</span>
          </td>
          <td class="text-start">Checkpoint Submission</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="text-start">
            <span class="fw-bold">November</span>
          </td>
          <td class="text-start">
            Winners announcement and presentation of prizes will be announced in
            November in conjunction with the Bataan Governor's Office and the
            Bataan Health Promotion Board
          </td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </div>
</div>

