<div id="judging" class="pt-5"></div>
<div data-aos="flip-right" class="px-md-4 py-2 m-md-5 m-3 text-center">
  <h2 class="fs-2 pt-5 pb-3 font-3">Judging Criteria</h2>
  <div class="table-responsive px-md-3">
    <table class="table table-bordered">
      <thead>
        <tr class="table-dark font-3">
          <th scope="col">Criteria</th>
          <th scope="col">Below Expectations</th>
          <th scope="col">Meeting Expectations</th>
          <th scope="col">Exceeding Expectations</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody class="font-3 text-center">
        <tr>
          <td class="text-start">
            <span class="fw-bold">Explanation of TFG Concept(s)</span>
          </td>
          <td>
            TFG concepts are vaguely and broadly mentioned, with little to no
            support using examples and contextualisation.
          </td>
          <td>
            TFG concepts are explained accurately and fully. Explanation is
            understandable.
          </td>
          <td>
            TFG concepts are explained accurately and fully. Content is further
            supported with appropriate examples and graphics.
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="text-start fw-bold">Creativity</td>
          <td>
            Video incorporates basic creative elements that slightly capture the
            audience’s attention.
          </td>
          <td>
            Video incorporates good creative elements that keep the audience
            engaged from time to time.
          </td>
          <td>
            Video incorporates outstanding creative elements that keep the
            audience fully engaged.
          </td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </div>
</div>

